OL,6,FElliot Archer, an inspector for the
OL,7,FHealth and Safety Executive, said:
OL,8,F"This tragic incident should be a
OL,9,Freminder to the waste industry not to
OL,10,Fbecome complacent with the risks
OL,11,Fworkplace transport poses."
OL,13,FThe HSE investigation found CCTV
OL,14,Ffootage from the week before the
OL,15,Fincident showed it was common for
OL,16,Fpeople on site to bypass segregated
OL,17,Fpedestrian routes, with some seen
OL,18,Fclimbing over barriers that were
OL,19,Fintended to keep them safe.
