OL,3,CWaste company fined #2.48m after
OL,4,Cworker killed by reversing truck
OL,6,FControl measures were in place to
OL,7,Fallow pedestrians and vehicles to move
OL,8,Fsafely, but a lack of monitoring and
OL,9,Fsupervision allowed poor working
OL,10,Fpractices to develop between the
OL,11,Fworkers on site, Leeds Magistrates
OL,12,FCourt heard.
OL,14,FMr Archer said: "Our investigation
OL,15,Ffound a casual attitude to health and
OL,16,Fsafety with workers treating a high
OL,17,Fhazard site like a playground.
OL,19,F"Nearly a quarter of all deaths
OL,20,Finvolving workplace transport occur
OL,21,Fduring reversing manoeuvres."
